title: Is Jax The Correct 'Firestorm' Match For Dr. Stein In Oct. 27 Episode Of 'The Flash'?
text: Is Jax The Correct 'Firestorm' Match For Dr. Stein In Oct. 27 Episode Of 'The Flash'? Friday, 23 October 2015 (17 minutes ago) Among the exciting things about "The Flash" is the Flash Universe and meeting other speedsters. It was confirmed that the two speedsters who will drop in are Zoom and Firestorm. For Zoom, viewers will have to wait a bit longer, but Firestorm might debut in the next episode titled, "The Fury of Firestorm." The Flash S02x04 The Fury of Firestorm - Trailer 00:21 Plot Synopsis: "Barry (Grant Gustin) and the team look for another Firestorm match for Dr. Stein (Victor Garber). When the team meets Jefferson “Jax” Jackson (guest star Franz Drameh), Caitlin (Danielle Panabaker) has her reservations about whether Jax is the right match for Dr. Stein. Iris...
